<FindBugsFilter xmlns="https://github.com/spotbugs/filter/3.0.0">
  <!--
    Reviewed suppressions (Chapter 16: suppress with a reason, never disable a whole detector).

    This module has NONE: that is the chapter's point made by the build. The model types are immutable
    records (Analyzer) and enums (Substrate, Moment, Concern), and LayeredStack holds only an EnumMap it
    never hands out by reference, so the representation-exposure detectors stay quiet without any
    suppression. The filter is kept (empty) so a future, genuinely-reviewed suppression has a home with a
    reason, rather than being added inline.
  -->
</FindBugsFilter>
